{
  "stem": "17301.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "How long did you stay in Neustadt-Glewe?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Neustadt-Glewe, we only stayed like three days, because we were so anxious to get out of there and-- and start the-- the journey back home, which we didn't know which way to go.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had no idea where we were.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, you know, we found out that we were next to Hamburg.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, I wasn't going to go to Hamburg, because going back to Czechoslovakia is the opposite way.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we start.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We asked somebody which way is south to go down south.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he told us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we start to walk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And as we were walking, we encountered-- [SIGHS] we were like 10 of us, 10 girls.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And all of a sudden in the distance we saw Russian soldiers, Cossacks.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my mother had a horrible, horrible story to tell us about Cossacks, how, you know, they rape women and-- and they're very mean.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I was very apprehensive of even talking to them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They came close, and one stopped.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The commander of-- of that unit stopped and started to talk to me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I told him, I said, [NON-ENGLISH], which is means Jewish, Jewish.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he just didn't understand what it is.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Anyway, finally, he realized that we were Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I told him-- I showed him my-- my number on my arm.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he didn't know what the number was because he never saw it before.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I couldn't explain it to him because I spoke a Russian, but not such a wonderful Russian that I was able to explain everything to him.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He went, and he took everybody's drink-- what do you-- they have it in their-- I don't know-- what they carry.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Their canteen, whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
